Body: Description: We have a denylist that has been working fine. Today, I check the logs and there is so many Content Threat Blocked for Facebook.com. It shows the majoiry for a user we have, and it also shows for me. I am not even visiting facebook and the user isnt visiting facebook too. How can we stop the spam from showing up, this didn't happen before.
